Package com.modern.codes.lime.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyExistsException
    thrown when an entity with at leas one unique field already exists .
    ForbiddenException
    thrown when eg. an authentication attempt is not allowed with the given credentials (not details returned).
    IllegalDataException
    thrown when the given data is not valid in the current context.
    InvalidRequestException
    thrown when a request is invalid in the current context.
    NotAcceptableException
    exception, thrown when given data is not acceptable.
    NotFoundException
    thrown when an entity is not found where it is expected.
    OperationNotAllowedException
    thrown when a contract management API call is not allowed.
    ServiceUnavailableException
    The type Service unavailable exception.
    StorageException
    The type Storage exception.
    StorageFileNotFoundException
    The type Storage file not found exception.
    UnprocessableEntityException
    thrown when an entity contains validation errors.
